## Shared Components

Build these first. Every onboarding screen reuses them.

### Button (4 states)
Width 100%, radius 14px, font 13px/19.5px DM Sans, inline-flex center, gap 8px.
- Primary: bg `--accent`, text `--white`, weight 500, padding 16px h / 14px v
- Disabled: bg `--bg-input`, text `--text-muted`, weight 500, padding 16px h / 14px v
- Outline: bg `--bg-input`, border 1px `--border`, text `--text-secondary`, weight 500, padding 16px h / 14px v
- Ghost: transparent, text `--text-muted`, weight 400, padding 16px h / 4px v

### OnboardingHeader
Width 100%, padding-bottom 8px, space-between center.
Logo group centered: 18×17 icon (fill --text-primary, glow shadow) + "Grain" DM Serif Text 18px, gap 8px.
- header-logo: logo centered, no back arrow
- header-logo-back: 20×20 back arrow (stroke 2px --text-secondary) + centered logo

### ProgressBar
Separate from header. 24px padding-top, 8px padding-bottom.
Active: 24×4px --accent, radius 2px. Inactive: 8×4px --border, radius 2px. Gap 8px.

### Chip (4 variants)
Radius 22px, font 13px/19.5px DM Sans.
- Unselected: bg --bg-card, border 1px --border, text --text-secondary 400, padding 16px h / 10px v
- Selected: bg --accent-soft, border 1.5px --accent, text --accent 400, padding 16px h / 10px v
- Static: bg --bg-elevated, no border, text --text-secondary 400, padding 12px h / 4px v
- ChipButton: transparent, border 1.5px --border, text --text-secondary 400, padding 12px h / 10px v, plus icon
  - “Custom” chip in Log/Onboarding uses dashed outline when specified by design

### HourBlock
Padding 14px h / 8px v, radius 8px, font 13px/19.5px 500.
- Unselected: transparent, border 1px --border, text --text-muted
- Selected: transparent, border 1px --accent, text --accent

### SummaryCard
Bg --bg-card, border 1px --border, radius 14px, padding 16px h / 18px v.
Header: label 10px 600 uppercase --text-muted (ls 0.12px) + Edit 10px 600 uppercase --accent. Gap 12px to content.

### Drawer
Bg --bg-card, top-radius 22px, border 1px --border, 24px horizontal padding.
Close: right-aligned X icon, 24px top / 8px bottom padding. Slide-up animation.
Elevated surfaces in light mode may use `--shadow-elevated` instead of heavy borders.

### TextInput / TextArea
Width 100%, padding 16px, bg --bg-input, radius 14px, font 13px/19.5px 400.
Focus: border 1px or ring using `--accent-glow` (and in light mode may use `--shadow-input-focus`).
TextArea min-height 120px.

